transcripts: This is the Deluxe Hi-Reach cleaning kit from Bed Bath and Beyond. The cleaning kit is a cost effective solution for homes with high ceilings and allows you to access hard to reach places with ease. This cleaning kit includes a clamp bulb changer, squeegee and microfiber scrubber, a bendable duster, cobweb duster, broken bulb changer, suction bulb changer and a eight foot L telescoping pole. The pole allows you to reach up to fourteen feet and easily retracts for convenient storage when not in use. The Deluxe Hi-Reach cleaning kit available online or at a Bed Bath and Beyond near you.
